                        class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight"
                    >
                        Make five thoughtful comments today.
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mt-3 text-zinc-300">
                        Check what changes in a week.
                    </p>
                    <div class="mt-6 flex justify-center gap-3">
